reviewText: kept me on the edge of my seat!! i gasped, booed and cringed all through this movie. once it was over i knew i had to buy it!!! i reccomend it!
This is an excellent Korean made suspense thriller that is a must see!!  Sue Ae, the main character, is absolutely phenomenal!!!  I HIGHLY RECOMMEND this movie.  One of my favorite Korean movies!
just saw this on youtube and it is now my favorite movie. definitely will be adding this to my colletion.
